  "subject": "Release version 1.1.1 of dockers and roll versions",
  "commit_message": "Release version 1.1.1 of dockers and roll versions\n\nRelease 1.1.1 version of dockers and roll versions.\nNote: the docker tag for dgbuilder and odlsli is slightly different\nfrom other containers - they both use 'SNAPSHOT' instead of 'STAGING'\nin order for CSIT test to work correctly.\n\nChange-Id: I0c13a2dad9553acfa813968c9bf42d6a008185dc\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-3179\nSigned-off-by: Dan Timoney <dtimoney@att.com>\n",
